        {
            "title": "財經｜據報Meta擬下月全球裁員一成涉近8,000人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜據報Meta擬下月全球裁員一成涉近8,000人\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜據報<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Meta\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Meta\">Meta</a>擬下月全球裁員一成涉近8,000人</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透》引述消息報道，Meta(美：META)計劃下月20日展開今年首波大規模裁員，後續還將有更多裁員行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息指，首輪裁員將裁減全球約10%員工，即近8,000人。公司並計劃下半年進一步裁員，但日期和規模等具體細節未定，高層或會按人工智能技術的發展情況調整計劃。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">早前有報道指Meta計劃裁減全球兩成或以上員工。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1meta%E6%93%AC%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1-%E6%88%90%E6%B6%89%E8%BF%918-000%E4%BA%BA-021029249.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 10:17:09",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財律指揮｜食兩家巨頭茶禮 走入AI圈核心  Marvell仍有上升空間 ｜曲鳴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/g6dbvKocwntS91uESZz_bQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/8262ccbf5f2a74f9fca79118e0283700\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊和談反反覆覆，與其估談判進展，不如回歸基本步，物色合適的股票去投資AI發展的大趨勢。在AI發展浪潮中，除了直接買科網巨頭，買入得到科網巨頭青睞的公司亦相當不錯，皆因前者會做足DD，證明技術水平值得合作。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Marvell\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Marvell;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Marvell\">Marvell</a>主打數據基建的半導體解決方案，近日接連得到英偉達20億美元戰略合作協議，又與Google商討TPU上的合作，證明其潛力相當不錯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前Marvell ASIC業務約15億美元，但與谷歌的合作便有高達20億美元的金額，無獨有偶，英偉達戰略投資了20億美元到Marvell，讓後者有足夠的現金拓展AI業務。實際上，以上兩間並非唯一與Marvell有關係的科網巨頭，Marvell與Amazon及微軟都有合作。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4e2580bd-ae33-38a7-b0a8-0f0f9b4cfa5d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然Marvell市值未算大，估值未必如一線巨頭般享有極高溢價，但在巨頭們的技術肯定、真金白銀支持下，Marvell 正由「組件供應商」轉型為「AI 基礎設施核心夥伴」。對於追求 AI 長線增長、又不想過度集中於單一顯卡龍頭的投資者而言，這類在科網巨頭處處逢源的半導體企業，不失為當前波動市中更具爆發力的選擇。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">公司股價若回至140美元附近的水平可以考慮買入，中線目標先博200元，若回至120元可加多一注。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E5%BE%8B%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE-%E9%A3%9F%E5%85%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD%E8%8C%B6%E7%A6%AE-%E8%B5%B0%E5%85%A5ai%E5%9C%88%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83-marvell%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93-%E6%9B%B2%E9%B3%B4-020000767.html",
